<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，威格先生散步后回到家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走进厨房给自己倒了杯橙汁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他听到卧室里有什么声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！咔嚓！咔嚓！嗡嗡！嗡嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事儿？”威格先生疑惑地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走进卧室，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房间里到处都是蜘蛛网，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>保险箱的门被打开了，里面是空的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”威格先生喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的钱全不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用了，谢谢。”一个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想买巧克力棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说完就把门关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们正在卖巧克力棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去下一家试试吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在为美罗城的贫困家庭筹钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个孩子来到了下一家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西敲了敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位老爷爷打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么事儿？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，爷爷！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你想买好吃的巧克力棒吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们有三种口味。所有的钱会......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃巧克力棒会长蛀牙的。”老爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从来不吃巧克力棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在为贫困家庭筹钱。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不感兴趣，而且我很忙。再见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他关上了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是太糟了！”大家离开房子时，杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没人买巧克力棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别着急。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还得继续努力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们该去别的小区。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是富人区。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肯定有人会买巧克力棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔的脸上露出笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个好主意。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们请火箭女孩儿帮我们卖巧克力棒吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“火箭女孩儿有什么办法？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不能强迫人家买东西啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也许是对的。”特勒尔叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去下一家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个朋友又走了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们走到下一家时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朋友们往门口走时，罗西停在人行道上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长！”罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道威格先生是谁吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然知道。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是美罗城最有钱的人之一。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我刚好在他家附近。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好！”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人闯进他家，偷走了钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长先生。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿会找到那个小偷的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>